  "22297b90-82a0-4f83-a09e-8ed92488b776"],
 " expands the coherent state into a more explicit form in terms of Boson or \
Fermion operators. Note that through the process, the Fock states below ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  RowBox[{
   TemplateBox[{
     Cell[
      TextData["Bottom"]], "paclet:ref/Bottom"},
    "RefLink",
    BaseStyle->{"InlineFormula"}], "[", 
   TemplateBox[{
     Cell[
      TextData["a"]], "paclet:QuantumMob/Q3/ref/a"},
    "RefLink",
    BaseStyle->{"InlineFormula", "TI"}], "]"}]], "InlineFormula",
  FontFamily->"Source Sans Pro",ExpressionUUID->
  "87b237f7-8714-4706-a507-1ca654a4761e"],
 " and above ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  RowBox[{
   TemplateBox[{
     Cell[
      TextData["Top"]], "paclet:ref/Top"},
    "RefLink",
    BaseStyle->{"InlineFormula"}], "[", 
   TemplateBox[{
     Cell[
      TextData["a"]], "paclet:QuantumMob/Q3/ref/a"},
    "RefLink",
